    <item>
      <title>菲律宾副总统杜特尔特准备为弹劾辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/philippines-vp-duterte-preparing-defense-against-impeachment-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾副总统萨拉·杜特尔特周三表示，她正在准备对针对她的弹劾指控进行辩护，但她对能否获得立法者足够的支持来对抗弹劾表示怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/philippines-vp-duterte-preparing-defense-against-impeachment-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 06:46:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿联酋敲定协议以促进与俄罗斯等国的贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/uae-finalizes-pact-to-boost-trade-with-nations-including-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿联酋与欧亚经济联盟达成经济协议，旨在通过降低关税和消除贸易壁垒来增加非石油双边贸易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/uae-finalizes-pact-to-boost-trade-with-nations-including-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 05:01:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨将请求信任投票，引发 2 月选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/scholz-to-request-confidence-vote-triggering-february-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨计划于周三向下议院提交一份请愿书，要求下周一进行信任投票，以引发 2 月底的提前选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/scholz-to-request-confidence-vote-triggering-february-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜首次就危机发表评论 抨击尹富强“独裁”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/north-korea-slams-yoon-dictatorship-in-first-comment-on-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周，朝鲜首次对韩国政治局势发表评论，谴责韩国总统尹锡烈试图实施戒严。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/north-korea-slams-yoon-dictatorship-in-first-comment-on-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 04:17:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国誓言回应加拿大因涉嫌侵犯人权而实施的制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/china-vows-response-to-canada-sanctions-for-alleged-rights-abuse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国谴责加拿大因涉嫌侵犯人权而对八名中国官员实施制裁，这导致本已紧张的双边关系出现新的裂痕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/china-vows-response-to-canada-sanctions-for-alleged-rights-abuse</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 04:16:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国将对威胁限制香港的美国官员实施签证限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/china-to-restrict-visas-to-us-officials-for-threatening-hk-curbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示，将对涉嫌干预香港事务的一些美国官员实施签证限制，这一针锋相对的举措凸显了唐纳德·特朗普上任前亚洲金融中心的地缘政治紧张局势加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/china-to-restrict-visas-to-us-officials-for-threatening-hk-curbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 04:05:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾继续进行调查，杜特尔特跳过质询</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/philippines-says-probe-to-go-ahead-as-duterte-skips-questioning</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾国家调查局将继续调查副总统萨拉·杜特尔特对总统费迪南德·马科斯发出的暗杀威胁，此前她周三第二次未出面接受问询。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/philippines-says-probe-to-go-ahead-as-duterte-skips-questioning</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 03:09:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国金融家尹永康寻求在调查升级之际继续抗争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/s-korea-s-yoon-prefers-impeachment-over-quitting-chosun-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管韩国总统尹锡烈的戒严宣言调查正在深入，且其所属党派的更多成员表示将支持弹劾，但他似乎决心继续战斗，而不是提前下台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/s-korea-s-yoon-prefers-impeachment-over-quitting-chosun-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 01:47:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国特使认为英国将领导与特朗普的欧洲关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/uk-should-lead-push-on-nato-spending-in-europe-us-envoy-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国驻英国大使简·哈特利表示，在特朗普重返白宫前夕，法国和德国仍在努力应对政治不稳定，英国有机会在欧洲与特朗普的关系中发挥主导作用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/uk-should-lead-push-on-nato-spending-in-europe-us-envoy-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 17:57:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙力图避免选举以遏制法国极右翼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/macron-aims-to-avoid-new-french-parliament-election-before-2027</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙 (Emmanuel Macron) 寻求组建一个能执政到 2027 年的温和派联盟，从而让政府摆脱国民联盟领袖玛丽娜·勒庞 (Marine Le Pen) 的控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/macron-aims-to-avoid-new-french-parliament-election-before-2027</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 17:25:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
